title: Ep 2434 - The Thankyou Gift
shortDesc: Athmaram has called over all the kids to give them a speech on how to tackle the pressure of exams. Meanwhile, others are giving Popatlal ideas that might help him tackle his marriage problem, but nothing pleases him.

shortDesc: Daya is finally returning back home and Jethalal and the rest of the society is happy to hear the news. But the Daya who has come back is lost in her thoughts of the past. Her tales of the sweet days past has left a smile on Jethalalâ€™s face.

title: Ep 2436 - Jethalals Scare
shortDesc: Jethalal is first stopped by Baga and Nattu Kaka from entering his own shop and blame it on his Kundali. Then Jethalal's brother-in-law Sunderlal lands up in the city and has come to take the most prized possession of Jethalal. This worries Jethalal.

title: Ep 2437 - A trees root
shortDesc: Sunder is in town. He calls Jethalal and asks to meet him but the scared Jethalal asks Taarak to come with him since he suspects he might get looted. Sunder thus meets them but gives them a riddle as he states his reason for visit.

title: Ep 2438 - Sunders Mischeif
shortDesc: When Sunder asks Jethalal to meet him, Jethalal refuses, saying he always takes money from him. However, Sunder replies that if he does not comply then he will lose someone close to him.

title: Ep 2439 - Whats Sunder Up To?
shortDesc: When Sunder asks Jethalal to meet him, Jethalal refuses, saying he always takes money from him. However, Sunder replies that if he does not comply then he will lose someone close to him.

title: Ep 2440 - The Dinner
shortDesc: Babita invites Jethalal and his family for dinner in her house and he agrees, but the same day Popatlal also invites Dada Ji and Tapu with their family to come to his house for dinner for which Dada Ji agrees to.

title: Ep 2441 - The Special Meal
shortDesc: Champaklal is hungry and so is Jethalal and Tappu. When Taarak arrives, Champaklal and his son and grandson have to be contempt with the healthy food prepared by Anjali. Later, all the Gokuldham society members have something planned for Jethalal.

title: Ep 2442 - Jethalals Breakfast
shortDesc: Anjali is overjoyed to see that Taarak has finished the salad she made for dinner. She later learns that Champaklal, Jethalal, and Tapu finished off the salad.

title: Ep 2443 - Champaklals Plan
shortDesc: Jethalal is ecstatic after learning that Baga has spoken with the caterer and has arranged food for Jethalal. Later, Champaklal notices that during the summer not only people but also the animals are dehydrated.

title: Ep 2444 - Champaklals Kind Gesture
shortDesc: Champaklal calls an urgent meeting at the Gokuldham society. He informs the society members about animals and humans suffering dehydration during summer.

title: Ep 2445 - The Strike
shortDesc: Popatlal learns that Bhide and Madhvi are attending a wedding. He too decides to accompany them in order to find a suitable bride for him at the wedding. Later, Jethalal learns that taxi and autorickshaw drivers have called a strike.

title: Ep 2446 - Destination
shortDesc: The Gokuldham society members are caught in a fix. There is a strike of taxis and auto-rickshaws and the society members cannot commute to their respective destinations. Finally. Sodhi comes to the rescue and drops each of them to their destination.

title: Ep 2447 - The Lift
shortDesc: Champaklal is in a hurry but neither are there any taxis nor any auto-rickshaws. Baga learns about Champaklalâ€™s problem and asks Bavri to give a lift to Champaklal. Seeing the trouble, Tappu decides to learn driving.

title: Ep 2448 - Sakaram in Trouble
shortDesc: Tappu has decided to learn how to drive. Unable to find a scooter to learn driving, Tappu zeroes in on Sakaram. He steals the scooterâ€™s key from Bhideâ€™s house in order to make a duplicate key. Will Bhide find out about Tappuâ€™s plan?
